name: Matthew Laude
bio: Matthew Laude graduated from Cairn University in 2019 with a degree in Music Education. He went on to work for a private school where he was the K-12 Music Teacher. In the wake of COVID-19, his school ended up having to shut down. Afterwards, Matthew decided to become a software engineer, attended General Assembly, and graduated in 2021. Matthew works hard to polish his CSS and React skills.
